Alerts
------
1. Status
    - [x] Print last 10 alerts sorted by age in check details
    - [x] Show latest alert directly in the service summary

3. Performance Metrics
    - [x] Amount of current alerts

4. Configurable Thresholds
    - [x] Amount of Alerts
    - [x] Make "Support bundle collection completed successfully" configurable (remove from list)

Ports
-----
1. Status
    - [x] Connected Port Status
    - [x] Port Errors (InvalidCrcCount, InvalidTransmissionWordCount, LinkFailureCount, LossOfSignalCount, LossOfSyncCount)

3. Performance Metrics
    - [x] Read / Write Throughput
    - [x] Read / Write IO/s
    - [x] Number of Port Errors

4. Configurable Thresholds
    - [x] Make port online / offline configurable
    - [x] Thresholds on Number of Port Errors

Virtual Disks
-------------
1. Status
    - [x] Disk status (Healthy, Offline, in Reclamation, in Recovery)
    - [x] Served status (served / unserved)

2. Information
    - [x] Size
    - [x] Recovery Priority
    - [x] Compression enabled
    - [x] Dedup enabled
    - [x] Encryption enabled
    - [x] Write Through enabled
    - [x] Sector Size

3. Performance Metrics
    - [x] Read / Write Throughput
    - [x] Read / Write IO/s

4. Configurable Thresholds
    - [x] Upper write IO
    - [x] Upper read IO
    - [x] Upper read latency
    - [x] Upper write latency
    - [x] Expected mapping state (served / not served)
    - [x] Expected path state (Path Down)

